snippet: In the extravaganza known as New York Fashion Week, it’s Mercedes-Benz Fashion Week versus MADE Fashion Week, an upstart rival.
abstract: Mercedes-Benz Fashion Week, official New York Fashion Week, is facing competition from five-year-old upstart MADE Fashion Week, represented by Creative Artists Agency; former has been experiencing something of identity crisis, criticized for being an overbranded trade show, but latter has been enjoying growing following as hipper, purer event, while still managing to lure big-name commercial partners.
lead_paragraph: In the extravaganza known as New York Fashion Week, it’s Mercedes-Benz Fashion Week versus MADE Fashion Week, an upstart rival.

headline.main: Rival Shows Vie for Relevancy in Fashion Week
